    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/vad-cou2-minimal-accepted-2026",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-lab-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Under ProfileMinimal review, the seven assessed credibility factors all meet or exceed their required gradation levels. The six unassessed factors are acknowledged as epistemic gaps documented in the bound Claim and Requirement nodes, where the intended-use scope (Class III VAD, absolute hemolysis prediction, MRL 5) is fully described. The assessment team accepts the package at the Minimal profile tier pending a future Complete-profile reassessment that formally links a structured Context of Use object and closes the model form and use error gaps.",
